{"tid":1263820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾籌登報資訊 III","createTime":"2019-06-28T11:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T15:17:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"defb03f9152bbca53f6ceec3f1b978b219d5f858","tid":1263820,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"大家或已發現，今天早上的《紐約時報國際版》已在全球多個國家發行，為香港人發聲。<br />\n<br />\n就在G20首日議程快將結束之時，位於地球另一邊的報章將會接力刊登我們的公開信，延續自由的火炬。而昨日錯過了《環球郵報》的朋友們不必灰心，我們已延長與《環球郵報》的合作──今天在加拿大多個城市，仍然可以看到香港人的身影。<br />\n<br />\n最新確認：<br />\n- 🇺🇸 美國 《華盛頓郵報》Washington Post ﹑《紐約時報(國際版)》The New York Times <br />\n- 🇨🇦 加拿大《環球郵報》 The Globe and Mail<br />\n<br />\n讓香港人的聲音傳遍世界，讓世人的支持匯聚我城。<br />\n<br />\n我們誠邀身在外地的各位與國際朋友分享公開信，並發揮創意，「用自己方法」以當地地標作背景為相關報章拍照 ，公開發佈至各社交媒體及標注 #FreedomHK，或把照片inbox 給我們。<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望大家現身支持晚上7時於立法會示威區（煲底）舉行的「連結G20・民主香港集會」，自己香港自己救。香港人，今晚見！"},{"pid":"cb83d05fd9cd7f76c9bb7006368a25b95138b22b","tid":1263820,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb8a6d737732f02d478360944a286de2cb8f8d7","tid":1263820,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmkOewg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmkOewg.jpg&h=3e7539f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a662a12f6d4deb7e408da8740042830cc9df3c7","tid":1263820,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0abb782aaaef0ad2350ccb2b40174f238b97a9cd","tid":1263820,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"想問下西班牙趕唔切出 <br />\n咁之後仲會唔會登?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ccef9530975fd6b5ec356e4fbed34b579c8461","tid":1263820,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}